@page "/"

<PageTitle>CloudVideoPlayer Demo — Overview</PageTitle>

<div class="page-header">
    <h1>CloudVideoPlayer Demo</h1>
    <p>
        A focused playground for <code>CloudComponents.VideoPlayer</code>. Use the navigation on
        the left to explore different scenarios.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">What you can try</h2>
    <p class="card-subtitle">Each page demonstrates a distinct feature set.</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Player</strong> — Standard MP4 playback with full controls, settings, and fullscreen.</li>
        <li><strong>Live Stream</strong> — HLS live-stream playback using the built-in HLS.js integration.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">Quick usage</h2>
    <p class="card-subtitle">Add the component to your Blazor page:</p>
    <pre><code>@("<VideoPlayer Metadata=\"Metadata\" />")</code></pre>
</div>
